products.title: Luna Softshade Jet Black Day And Night Blind
products.description: Make an update that will benefit the look and feel of your interior with this practical day and night roller blind. The luna softshade jet black day and night roller blind is designed with flexibility in mind. It can be fully opened or closed just like a standard day and night roller blind as well as adjusted to a semi closed position that enables both natural light penetration and privacy. Product id: db-vrbx1862 fabric colour: jet black material: 100% polyester headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white brackets control type: smooth continuous-looped chain energy saving rating: er1 - lowest energy saving value - due to blind type or fabric light filtering: yes luna softshade jet black day and night blind in black.
